{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"MathML","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/MathML","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"mathml-referenzen","title":"MathML-Referenzen","isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>Mathematical Markup Language (MathML)</strong> ist eine&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XML\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">XML (en-US)</a> (Extensible Markup Language) zur bildlichen Darstellung und strukturellen Beschreibung von mathematischen Termen und Gleichungen. Hier finden Sie Links zu Dokumentationen, Beispielen und Tools, die Ihnen helfen, mit dieser Technologie zu arbeiten. Für einen schnellen Überblick, schauen Sie sich die <a href=\"http://fred-wang.github.io/MozSummitMathML/index.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">slides for the innovation fairs at Mozilla Summit 2013</a> an.</p>\n\n<div class=\"row topicpage-table\" id=\"sect1\">\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"sect2\">\n\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"mathml-elementreferenz\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element\" title=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element\">MathML-Elementreferenz</a></dt>\n <dd>Details zu allen MathML-Elementen und Kompatibilitätsinformationen für Desktop- und Mobilbrowser.</dd>\n <dt id=\"mathml-attributreferenz\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute\" title=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute\">MathML-Attributreferenz</a></dt>\n <dd>Informationen über MathML-Attribute, um Darstellung oder Verhalten der Elemente zu beeinflussen.</dd>\n <dt id=\"mathml-beispiele\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Examples\" title=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Examples\">MathML-Beispiele</a></dt>\n <dd>MathML-Beispiele, die Ihnen zu verstehen helfen, wie es funktioniert.</dd>\n <dt id=\"mathml_in_der_praxis\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Authoring\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">MathML in der Praxis (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Vorschläge und Tipps, um in MathML zu schreiben, einschließlich MathML-Editoren und Hinweise, wie man die Ergebnisse in Web-Inhalt einfügt.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<p><a href=\"/de/docs/tag/MathML\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">Alles anzeigen...</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"sect3\">\n<h2 id=\"hilfe_von_der_gemeinschaft_bekommen\">Hilfe von der Gemeinschaft bekommen</h2>\n\n<ul>\n <li>Mozilla-Foren konsultieren<br>\n  <ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://lists.mozilla.org/listinfo/dev-tech-mathml\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Mailing-Liste</a></li>\n  \n  \n  <li><a href=\"https://groups.google.com/group/mozilla.dev.tech.mathml\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Newsgroup</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://groups.google.com/group/mozilla.dev.tech.mathml/feeds\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web-Feed</a></li>\n</ul></li>\n <li><a class=\"link-irc\" href=\"irc://irc.mozilla.org/%23mathml\" rel=\"external\" title=\"irc://irc.mozilla.org/%23mathml\">IRC channel</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"link-https external\" href=\"https://wiki.mozilla.org/MathML:Home_Page\" rel=\" noopener\">Wiki der Mozilla-Unterstützer</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/Math/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">W3C Math Home</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/www-math/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">www-math w3.org mail archive</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"tools\">Tools</h2>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"http://validator.w3.org\" rel=\" noopener\">W3C Validator</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"link-https external\" href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/de/firefox/addon/8969/\" rel=\" noopener\">FireMath Firefox add-on</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/collections/fred_wang/mathzilla/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Mathzilla Firefox add-on collection</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://github.com/fred-wang/TeXZilla\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">TeXZilla</a> - Javascript LaTeX to MathML Konverter (<a href=\"http://fred-wang.github.io/TeXZilla/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">live demo</a>, <a href=\"http://r-gaia-cs.github.io/TeXZilla-webapp/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Firefox OS webapp</a>, <a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/texzilla/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Firefox add-on</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/fred-wang/TeXZilla/wiki/Using-TeXZilla\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">using in a Web Page, JS program etc</a>)</li>\n <li><a href=\"https://dlmf.nist.gov/LaTeXML/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">LaTeXML</a> - übersetzt LaTeX-Dokumente in HTML+MathML Web-Seiten</li>\n <li><a href=\"http://webdemo.visionobjects.com/home.html#equation\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Equation</a> - übersetzt handgeschriebene Gleichungen in MathML oder LaTeX</li>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.mathjax.org/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathJax</a> - Cross-browser JavaScript display engine für mathematische Ausdrücke. Um MathJax zu zwingen, natives MathML zu nutzen, versuche <a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/mathjax-native-mathml/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">dieses Mozilla Add-on</a>, diese <a href=\"http://fred-wang.github.io/mathjax-native-mathml-safari/mathjax-native-mathml.safariextz\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Safari-Erweiterung</a> oder dieses <a href=\"https://openuserjs.org/scripts/fred.wang/MathJax_Native_MathML/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">GreaseMonkey-Skript</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"verwandte_inhalte\">Verwandte Inhalte</h2>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS\" title=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS\">CSS</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML\" title=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/SVG\" title=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG\">SVG</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser-kompatibilität","title":"Browser-Kompatibilität","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect4\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect5\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Merkmal</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Allgemeine Unterstützung</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span> [1]</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/1.5\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2005-11-25.\">1.5</a> (1.8)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span> [1]</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Merkmal</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Allgemeine Unterstützung</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.8)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] Verfügbar durch plug-in(s).</p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"MathML-Referenzen","id":"mathml-referenzen"},{"text":"Browser-Kompatibilität","id":"browser-kompatibilität"}],"summary":"Mathematical Markup Language (MathML) ist eine XML (en-US) (Extensible Markup Language) zur bildlichen Darstellung und strukturellen Beschreibung von mathematischen Termen und Gleichungen. Hier finden Sie Links zu Dokumentationen, Beispielen und Tools, die Ihnen helfen, mit dieser Technologie zu arbeiten. Für einen schnellen Überblick, schauen Sie sich die slides for the innovation fairs at Mozilla Summit 2013 an.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"MathML","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"MathML","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"MathML","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"MathML","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"MathML","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"MathML","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"MathML","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"MathML","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"MathML","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"MathML","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/mathml","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/mathml/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/MathML","title":"MathML"}],"pageTitle":"MathML | MDN","noIndexing":false}}